<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">采蘋</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0542f2d34e65">
于以采蘋？南涧之滨。于以采藻？于彼行潦。<br />于以盛之？维筐及筥。于以湘之？维锜及釜。<br />于以奠之？宗室牖下。谁其尸之？有齐季女。
</div>
</div>
