she gathers the large duckweed ,<br />by the banks of the stream in the southern valley .<br />she gathers the pondweed ,<br />in those pools left by the floods .<br />she deposits what she gathers ,<br />in her square baskets and round ones<br />she boils it ,in her tripods and pans .<br />she sets
